race.comment: VERY TORQUEE (6) is overdue and deserves a win. Has placed three of four so far including 2/2 here. Drawn to take a sit with some cover and looks hard to hold out. SILVER TOP RIDGE (9) tried to lead throughout on debut at Wangaratta and was just nabbed late. Given a break and returns on home track. Tricky gate but expected to give a sight. TALLINGAS IMMORTAL (12) raced just once last campaign for a narrow second. Prior to that was competitive in open two-year-old class. Placed 2/2 fresh and rates a leading player. DIVINE BELLINI (14) settled off pace on the inside at debut and only boxed home. Better for the experience and can improve sharply. Stablemate PRINCE OF LOVE (4) makes debut. By Prince Of Caviar out of She's Our Rippa and presents on the back of two jump outs. Watch for market moves.
